501
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:05,699
Jung Min.

502
00:42:05,699 --> 00:42:07,295
Turunkan aku di depan.

503
00:42:32,199 --> 00:42:34,135
Kau baik-baik saja?

504
00:42:34,135 --> 00:42:35,858
Dia hanya mengirim ikan teri.

505
