510
00:42:50,500 --> 00:42:52,800
Direktur Choi merasa sangat terancam.

511
00:42:53,699 --> 00:42:55,969
Dia akan dipecat, atas keinginan Pimpinan Yoon.

512
00:42:58,800 --> 00:43:00,400
Apa?

